  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients &gt;=18 years

          -  diagnosed of calcifying shoulder tendinitis diagnosed by a medical specialist
             (rehabilitation, orthopedic surgeon or rheumatologist) by x-ray

          -  with disease evolution of more than 3 months and less than 12 months

          -  that give their informed consent by writing

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Previous shoulder surgery patients

          -  Patients with shoulder affections treated with shockwaves or corticosteroid
             injections.
      </textblock>
